\pard\ltrpar\cf1\b\f0\fs20 Magic provides functions to manage multiple parallel programs at one time.\par
\par
In this example, several parallel programs are started when this task starts. Pressing the View Programs button will display the parallel programs, and show their status. You can close or kill the programs, using push buttons.\par
\par
Note: To run the parallel programs, the Deployment Mode setting must be set to Background. This sample will only run when executed from a runtime engine (not from the studio)\par
